Edition:
Quote:   [=CRUSH PEN] Receiving yards. These must have the capacity to take incoming mobs. They communicate with the forwarding yards, or diamond pens, which are much smaller, and lead up to the crush pens or forcing pens. ...  These last [crush pens or forcing pens] are usually one or two long pens that communicate by a two-way gate with the mouth of the drafting race.
